summary: Peter: *coming back to the little group of Avengers that are "dead"* Well this sucks even more now. I searched and searched and...
body:
Peter: *coming back to the little group of Avengers that are “dead”* Well this sucks even more now. I searched and searched and none of my friends are dead, not even Ned.

Strange: I dont see how that is a bad thing?

Peter: Ned is my best friend. If I die, he’s dying with me.

Bucky *proudly*: I understood that reference

Everyone looks at him with raised eyebrows

Bucky: What? Shuri explained that part of my rehabilitation is reintroduction into the modern society and that apperently includes pop culture.

T'Challa *lying face down on the floor*: That little shit. When I asked her to explain Vines to me, she told me I was too old.

Bucky: I love Vines. My favorite is the one where the guy makes fun of Steve.

Peter and Bucky *with a bad German accents*: How did we take down Captain America? We shot him in ze legs because hiz shield is zi size of a dinner plate and he iz an idiot.

Sam: The language is English but I didn’t understand a word they said

T'Challa: Welcome to the club!

Peter: *kicks floor* No one from my class is here. Balance my ass.

Strange: I don’t understand kids these days. All they want is to die and make obscure references

Peter: That’s not tru… Yeah, pretty much. Yes!

Wanda *lying on the floor, staring into the void abover her, scoffs*: In my case, everyone around me dies

Quill: Same

Drax: It’s the same for me.

Peter: Well, this got pretty dark pretty fast

Strange: We are dead. It doesn’t get any darker than that. And by the way you started it.

Peter: I’m sorry. I am just so bored and confused. Like, if we are dead dead, then why are we not cured. Why is Mr. Barnes still missing an arm? Is his arm in hell? Or is this hell and his arm is in heaven?

Wanda *still on the floor, singing*: Spiderman, spiderman, does whatever a philosopher can…

summary: Those are the concept for my MCU Spider-Man logos. I started to work on my own Spider-Man logo back in January. The first one...
body: Those are the concept for my MCU Spider-Man logos. I started to work on my own Spider-Man logo back in January. The first one was based on the PS4 Spider-Man logo. Then by March-April, I came up with a new one. This is loosely based on the Sam Raimi one, albeit with the legs being taller. When the summer came, I officially redesigned the logo. Like my first redesign, it was based on the Raimi one.
